name: Xena: Warrior Princess: The Talisman of Fate
name_original: Xena: Warrior Princess: The Talisman of Fate
description: Xena: Warrior Princess: The Talisman of Fate is a 1999 fighting video game developed by Saffire Corporation and published by Titus Software for the Nintendo 64. It is based on the television series, Xena: Warrior Princess, which aired from 1995 to 2001.
